              <h2>Bootstrap WordPress Theme &#8211; BootWord &#8211; Responsive &#038; Simple</h2>
              
                <p class="meta"><i class="icon-calendar"></i> 19 Oct 12 - <i class="icon-user"></i> Asho - <i class="icon-comment"></i> <a href="http://responsivewebinc.com/wordpress-themes/bootstrap-wordpress-theme-bootword-responsive-simple/#comments" title="Comment on Bootstrap WordPress Theme &#8211; BootWord &#8211; Responsive &amp; Simple">1 Comment</a></p>


                <p><a href="http://responsivewebinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/bootstrap-wordpress1.png"><img src="http://responsivewebinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/bootstrap-wordpress1.png" alt="bootstrap wordpress theme" title="bootstrap wordpress" width="550" height="220" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-333" /></a></p>
<p>Here i feel very happy to release my first WordPress theme which is fully customizable via Theme options panel. BootWord is a Boostrap based Responsive WordPress theme which supports all features of Bootstrap. It also supports font awesome icons, google web fonts and much more. The main highlight of this theme is its theme options panel. It allow you to edit all parts of your theme on the fly. So don&#8217;t worry if you don&#8217;t know programming. This design suits best for blogs or business sites.</p>
<p>Here are the full list of features of BootWrod:<br />
1. Professional Green design with background patterns.<br />
2. The design is simple and minimal.<br />
3. Fully responsive. Works great in Computers, Phones and Tablets.<br />
4. Supports Theme options panel. No coding skill needed.<br />
5. Upload logo and favicon easily using media uploader.<br />
6. Supports custom WordPress menu. Add links, pages, categories, etc., on the fly. Don&#8217;t forget that this theme supports drop down menu.<br />
7. Supports slider in home page. The great news is, you can add slider easily from theme options panel. No coding.<br />
8. Featured image for each post. This improves the look of your blog.<br />
9. Supports more than 200 font awesome icon.<br />
10. Supports social media icons. Again fully manageable via options panel.<br />
11. It has 4 widget area and supports tons of widgets.<br />
12. Professional footer area.<br />
13. Supports multi level comments. Best place to have debate.<br />
14. Supports google web fonts. </p>
<h4>Bootstrap WordPress theme</h4>
<p>If you are very eager to try out this theme, then check out our <a href="https://wrapbootstrap.com/theme/bootstrap-wordpress-theme-responsive-WB026N02G?ref=ashobiz">demo</a>. I am sure that you will love this theme. </p>
<p><strong>Color</strong> &#8211; Green, Black and White</p>
<p><strong>Doc </strong>- <a href="http://responsivewebinc.com/premium/bootword/doc/">http://responsivewebinc.com/premium/bootword/doc/</a></p>
<p><a href="http://responsivewebinc.com/premium/wp/bootword.zip" class="btn btn-danger">Download Bootstrap WordPress theme</a></p>
                
